      "body" : "@laanwj I did not include a fix for the sort issue #4274 here, that can be a separate PR or I can add another commit on this one.\r\n\r\nThe material I prepared on the guide is fully auditable and allows almost completely automated gitian builds leveraging Docker + LXC containers, this is easier and quicker than the VirtualBox VM approach, that's why I am proposing to add it; see also [the diagram](https://github.com/gdm85/tenku/blob/master/docker/gitian-host/diagram.png). I am confident that this will be helpful to developers and allow them to easily make more deterministic builds.",
